\begin_layout Subsection
ART TrackPack4
\begin_inset CommandInset label
LatexCommand label
name "sub:ART-TrackPack4"

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
An infrared optical tracking system to provide position and orientation
 tracking of one or more targets in the space.
 It consists of four cameras mounted around the top of the volume, an 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand nameref
reference "sub:ARTtrack-Controller/TP"

\end_inset

 computer, and a number of tracking targets.
 The tracking cameras have one red LED lit when they are inactive, and two
 red LEDs lit when they are active.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
See also 
