 More functionality is available, but it is not needed for use with the
 four existing tracking targets.
\begin_inset Marginal
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout
The DTrack2 software is installed on both the head and render node in Windows,
 but is typically only used on the head node.
 Tracking data is sent to both nodes regardless of where DTrack2 is run.
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

